	<article id="post-516" class="post-516 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-controinformazione category-esteri category-europa category-rivoluzioni category-terza-guerra-mondiale">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.hescaton.com/wordpress/dopo-lucraina-la-russia-rischia-la-disintegrazione/" title="Permalink a La Russia verso la frammentazione?" rel="bookmark">La Russia verso la frammentazione?</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://www.hescaton.com/wordpress/dopo-lucraina-la-russia-rischia-la-disintegrazione/" title="15:53" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2014-02-24T15:53:21+00:00">24 febbraio 2014</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.hescaton.com/wordpress/author/fenrir/" title="Visualizza tutti gli articoli di Fenrir" rel="author">Fenrir</a></span></span>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
						<div class="comments-link">
				<a href="http://www.hescaton.com/wordpress/dopo-lucraina-la-russia-rischia-la-disintegrazione/#comments" title="Commenti a La Russia verso la frammentazione?">6</a>			</div>
					</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<!-- Place this tag where you want the +1 button to render. -->
<div id="googleplussharebutton">
<div id="gp" class="g-plusone" data-annotation="inline" data-width="250"></div>

<!-- Place this tag after the last +1 button tag. -->
<script type="text/javascript">
  window.___gcfg = {lang: 'it'};

  (function() {
