<div class="addtoany_share_save_container addtoany_content_bottom"><div class="a2a_kit a2a_kit_size_32 addtoany_list a2a_target" id="wpa2a_7"><a class="a2a_button_facebook" href="http://www.addtoany.com/add_to/facebook?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hescaton.com%2Fwordpress%2Fcose-la-democrazia-il-paradosso-della-democrazia-che-perde-di-significato-e-si-fa-totalitarismo%2F&amp;linkname=Cos%E2%80%99%C3%A8%20la%20democrazia%3F%20Il%20paradosso%20della%20democrazia%20che%20perde%20di%20significato%20e%20si%20fa%20totalitarismo" title="Facebook" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_button_twitter" href="http://www.addtoany.com/add_to/twitter?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hescaton.com%2Fwordpress%2Fcose-la-democrazia-il-paradosso-della-democrazia-che-perde-di-significato-e-si-fa-totalitarismo%2F&amp;linkname=Cos%E2%80%99%C3%A8%20la%20democrazia%3F%20Il%20paradosso%20della%20democrazia%20che%20perde%20di%20significato%20e%20si%20fa%20totalitarismo" title="Twitter" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_button_google_plus" href="http://www.addtoany.com/add_to/google_plus?linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hescaton.com%2Fwordpress%2Fcose-la-democrazia-il-paradosso-della-democrazia-che-perde-di-significato-e-si-fa-totalitarismo%2F&amp;linkname=Cos%E2%80%99%C3%A8%20la%20democrazia%3F%20Il%20paradosso%20della%20democrazia%20che%20perde%20di%20significato%20e%20si%20fa%20totalitarismo" title="Google+" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"></a><a class="a2a_dd addtoany_share_save" href="http://www.addtoany.com/share_save"></a></div></div>					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
