						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://www.hescaton.com/wordpress/guerra-civile-globale-linstabilita-si-allarga/" title="11:17" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2014-01-11T11:17:02+00:00">11 gennaio 2014</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.hescaton.com/wordpress/author/fenrir/" title="Visualizza tutti gli articoli di Fenrir" rel="author">Fenrir</a></span></span>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
						<div class="comments-link">
				<a href="http://www.hescaton.com/wordpress/guerra-civile-globale-linstabilita-si-allarga/#comments" title="Commenti a Guerra Civile Globale: l&#8217;instabilità si allarga">6</a>			</div>
					</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<!-- Place this tag where you want the +1 button to render. -->
<div id="googleplussharebutton">
<div id="gp" class="g-plusone" data-annotation="inline" data-width="250"></div>

<!-- Place this tag after the last +1 button tag. -->
